text: Mariusz Fyrstenberg and Santiago González were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Andre Begemann and Jan-Lennard Struff won the title after defeating Carlos Berlocq and Andrés Molteni 6–3, 6–4 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Canberra Challenger - Doubles
